I waited for you.

01:37:30.554 --> 01:37:33.193
You shouldn't have come.

01:37:37.474 --> 01:37:41.626
What's going on Dolores? Is someone dead?
Granma Julia is alive?

01:37:42.074 --> 01:37:45.669
Alive! Can't you hear
