I won't die.

01:37:49.594 --> 01:37:52.108
Let's go.

01:37:59.794 --> 01:38:02.262
Wait. Dolores,
I don't understand anything.

01:38:02.994 --> 01:38:06.907
What don't you understand? You don't want
