02:04:27.597 --> 02:04:29.827
We have a big problem!

02:04:36.117 --> 02:04:37.948
We can't beat them.

02:04:40.997 --> 02:04:42.794
What's this guy whistling for?

02:04:42.997 --> 02:04:45.591
